---
import Base from "../../../layouts/Base.astro";
---
<Base title="Shopware" description="Shopware Rise, Evolve and Beyond for your business success in digital commerce – Hob by Horse.">
<div class="lp"><section class="hero"><div class="hi">
<p class="kicker">E-Commerce</p>
<h1>Shopware Rise, Evolve and Beyond for Your Business Success in Digital Commerce</h1>
<p>With the introduction of the new Shopware variants Rise, Evolve and Beyond, our partner is pursuing an innovative concept for increasing business success in digital commerce. The new plans offer comprehensive features that enable flexible design and individual development of online shops.</p>
</div></section>
<div class="content">
<h2>E-Commerce Developments with Shopware Plans Rise, Evolve and Beyond by Hob by Horse</h2>
<p>The new Shopware variants Rise, Evolve and Beyond represent virtual e-commerce tools that are the key to a successful launch of an online shop in digital commerce or the extension of an existing retail or wholesale business with an online shop version.</p>
<p>The Shopware plans offer a comprehensive toolkit that fundamentally provides all important functions for your individual shop requirements. Since the plans build on each other, you can grow at any time and adapt your shop system to your needs. We are thus ready to grow together!</p>

<h2>Using Shopware Strategically for Your Industry</h2>
<p>The three Shopware variants offer an optimal user experience for all target groups. Whether B2B or B2C, different market positions or market penetration – we support you in positioning your e-commerce strategically and achieving your goals.</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Shopware Rise</strong> – the ideal entry point into professional e-commerce</li>
<li><strong>Shopware Evolve</strong> – for growing online shops with advanced requirements</li>
<li><strong>Shopware Beyond</strong> – the enterprise solution for maximum flexibility and scalability</li>
</ul>
<p>Would you like to present your business model in a unique online shop and need individual developments with Shopware? Feel free to contact Hob by Horse by phone or email for advice on the options and features!</p>
</div></div>
</Base>
<style>
.lp{background:#1a1a1a;color:#fff;min-height:100vh}
.hero{padding-top:var(--header-height);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
.hi{max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:var(--spacing-3xl) 40px}
h1{font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.5rem);font-weight:800;line-height:1.15;color:#00b4d8;margin-bottom:var(--spacing-lg)}
.hero p:not(.kicker),.content p:not(.kicker){color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);line-height:1.75;text-align:left!important;max-width:none!important;margin-left:0!important;margin-right:0!important;margin-bottom:var(--spacing-md)}
.content{max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:var(--spacing-3xl) 40px var(--spacing-4xl)}
h2{font-size:var(--font-size-xl);font-weight:700;color:#E7007F;margin-top:var(--spacing-2xl);margin-bottom:var(--spacing-md);text-align:left!important}
ul{list-style:none;padding:0;margin-bottom:var(--spacing-lg)}
li{color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);line-height:1.7;padding-left:1.25rem;position:relative;margin-bottom:var(--spacing-md)}
li::before{content:"#";position:absolute;left:0;color:#E7007F;font-weight:700}
li strong{color:#fff}
</style>
